product.name: Brunello Cucinelli - Shearling Aviator Jacket
product.description: There are aviator jackets and then there's Brunello Cucinelli’s aviator jacket, which stands out thanks to the Italian label’s commitment to premium materials and craftsmanship. Made from sheepskin, it has a polished hide exterior and a generous shearling collar. The buckled straps and chunky silver zip add to its elevated feel.

product.name: Brunello Cucinelli - Suede Boots
product.description: EXCLUSIVE AT MR PORTER. Impeccable craftsmanship underpins every Brunello Cucinelli design, its collections are conceived in the hamlet of Solomeo, Umbria, and produced in and around Italy. Bridging the gap between smart and casual, these boots are made from smooth suede and set on durable commando-style rubber soles.

text_with_entities.text: EXCLUSIVE AT MR PORTER. caption.text:
There’s a winter wardrobe, and then there’s @brunellocucinelli_brand’s winter wardrobe. The Italian luxury leader has been producing finely crafted knitwear since 1978, and a few MR PORTER exclusives have just hit the shelves. So, stop fussing about what to wear during the colder months and let the experts dress you. 

Tap to show and head to the bio to discover the exclusive Brunello Cucinelli pieces on MR PORTER.

Words by: @lucyaaark
Photography by: @jamesrobjant
Styling by: @charlieschneiderjacobson

caption.text:
Gold PRX + green rubber strap = win? 🏆

I already know rose gold and green are a killer combo, but how does rose’s punchier sibling on the colour wheel fair? 

The @delugs “emerald green” rubber CTS strap for the PRX line is actually a deeper and more foresty green (vs the olive green of the standard line), which I think actually complements the sunnier yellow tones of this PRX quite well. It’s a louder combo for sure, but then again, anybody picking up the gold PRX ain’t looking for quiet. 

⌚️ @tissot_official PRX Powermatic 80 35mm T137.207.33.021.00
